Rose Hill (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rose_Hill_(actress) 0 Rose Lilian Hill (5 June 1914 – 22 December 2003) was an English actress and operatic soprano, who remains best known for her role as Madame Fanny La Fan in the British television series 'Allo 'Allo!. She was a former member of the Royal Shakespeare Company.
